description:
Danny welcomes Billie Lee, activist and Vanderpump Rules cast member, to the show. They talk dating, the current season, Tom's trumpet playing, and SO much more. Plus, Olympics correspondent Tyler Duckworth fills us in on sports, AND Danny talks about his Olympics, Sex and the City 3. PS The Billie Lee interview starts at 11:23 :)
